        ## Library Usage
            >>> from text_styler import TextStyler
        
            >>> styler = TextStyler()
            >>> converted = styler.convert("Hello World!")
            
            >>> print(converted)
            ð–§ð–¾ð”©ð–‘ð•  ð‘Šð™¤ð’“ð’ð˜¥
        
        ## Notes
        Only supported with Python3.
        
        
